{"tid":2199480,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"「反黑路人甲」原來世倫假死，驗完DNA真係蔣世龍","createTime":"2020-09-12T08:55:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-12T14:37:21.000Z","uid":43785,"like":10,"dislike":42,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"01aa13cffa6d472a3e1c9125c98ab25ed838964d","tid":2199480,"uid":43785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-12T08:55:03.000Z","msg":"王浩信死而復生驗DNA揭真正身份、老狐狸姜大衛成坐館 四聯幫面臨解散！<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.orientalsunday.hk/?p=394638&amp;utm_campaign=Sharing&amp;utm_medium=cpoy_url&amp;utm_source=cpoy_url\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.orientalsunday.hk%2F%3Fp%3D394638%26utm_campaign%3DSharing%26utm_medium%3Dcpoy_url%26utm_source%3Dcpoy_url&d=D4HIriwr0d5ovb2eA4y9f1cETUAZGKrTpJw0Ojiq68w%3D&h=861f080c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.orientalsunday.hk/?p=394638&amp;utm_campaign=Sharing&amp;utm_medium=cpoy_url&amp;utm_source=cpoy_url</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/htgUy2p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhtgUy2p.jpg&h=639f10a2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n王浩信驗完DNA揭開真相&mdash;&mdash;佢就係蔣世龍！被晨爺滅口前駕車逃走自爆「假死」！<br />\n<br />\n最後鐵頭想槍擊細倫，卻誤傷呀妹令她後腦受重創昏迷不醒。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/B4sTPFZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FB4sTPFZ.jpg&h=7960ee54&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nTVB真係老土到呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n手足，入來傾下劇情推下POST啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0cd329a3444a48300c5bd58be8968f863f2cc651","tid":2199480,"uid":261505,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-12T08:55:24.000Z","msg":"Yes Sir !<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9WVRM4c.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9WVRM4c.png&h=ec331784&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RUnkBNd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thu